<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Maolana Faozi | Digital Creative Portfolio</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap');
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; scroll-behavior: smooth; }
        .gradient-text {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #60a5fa, #a78bfa);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-900 text-slate-200">

    <header class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center px-6">
        <div class="max-w-4xl text-center">
            <h2 class="text-blue-400 font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Creative Professional</h2>
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Maolana Faozi</h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-400 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                Mahasiswa Sistem Informasi yang memadukan manajemen data dengan visi kreatif. Berbasis di <span class="text-white">Purwokerto</span>, menggerakkan solusi digital melalui visual dan teknologi.
            </p>
            <div class="flex justify-center gap-4">
                <a href="#about" class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full transition-all">Tentang Saya</a>
                <a href="#services" class="border border-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-800 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full transition-all">Layanan</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section id="about" class="py-20 bg-slate-800/50">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">Biografi Singkat</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
                        Lahir di <span class="text-blue-400">Purbalingga, 17 November 1996</span>, perjalanan saya adalah kombinasi antara dunia korporat dan industri kreatif. Sebagai seorang karyawan swasta sekaligus mahasiswa aktif, saya memahami pentingnya efisiensi dan estetika dalam setiap proyek.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-slate-300">
                        Saat ini, saya fokus mengembangkan ekosistem digital, baik melalui pengelolaan platform yayasan maupun bisnis kreatif mandiri.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-slate-700 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-600 shadow-xl">
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-slate-600 pb-2">
                            <span class="text-slate-400">Lokasi</span>
                            <span class="text-white">Purwokerto, ID</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-slate-600 pb-2">
                            <span class="text-slate-400">Pendidikan</span>
                            <span class="text-white">S1 Sistem Informasi</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-slate-600 pb-2">
                            <span class="text-slate-400">Fokus</span>
                            <span class="text-white">IT & Multimedia</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="services" class="py-20">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <h3 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Creative Business</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400">Layanan profesional untuk kebutuhan branding dan konten digital Anda.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div class="bg-slate-800 p-8 rounded-xl hover:translate-y-[-10px] transition-all border border-slate-700">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-camera-retro text-4xl text-blue-500 mb-6"></i>
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Photo & Videography</h4>
                    <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Menangkap momen dengan kualitas sinematik dan komposisi profesional.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-slate-800 p-8 rounded-xl hover:translate-y-[-10px] transition-all border border-slate-700">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-clapperboard text-4xl text-purple-500 mb-6"></i>
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Post Production</h4>
                    <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Editing video dan foto dengan sentuhan kreatif untuk media sosial maupun profesional.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-slate-800 p-8 rounded-xl hover:translate-y-[-10px] transition-all border border-slate-700">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-tower-broadcast text-4xl text-green-500 mb-6"></i>
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Live Streaming</h4>
                    <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Manajemen teknis siaran langsung untuk berbagai acara secara profesional.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 bg-blue-600">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Web Management</h3>
            <p class="text-blue-100 text-lg mb-8 italic">
                "Mengelola platform digital bukan sekadar coding, tapi tentang membangun kepercayaan. Bangga dipercaya untuk mengelola dan memelihara website yayasan sebagai kontribusi sosial."
            </p>
            <div class="inline-block bg-white text-blue-600 px-6 py-2 rounded-lg font-bold">
                Information System Student
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="py-12 border-t border-slate-800">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-4">&copy; 2026 Maolana Faozi. Built with passion in Purwokerto.</p>
            <div class="flex justify-center gap-6 text-slate-400">
                <a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition-colors"><i class="fa-brands fa-instagram text-xl"></i></a>
                <a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition-colors"><i class="fa-brands fa-linkedin text-xl"></i></a>
                <a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition-colors"><i class="fa-solid fa-envelope text-xl"></i></a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>

